      • Field

        public Field()

      • Field

        public Field(int id,
     java.lang.String title,
     int x_coord,
     int width,
     java.lang.String help_html,
     java.lang.String known_data)
        Creates a new field object based on the given parameters.
        Parameters:
        id - the field id
        title - the field title
        x_coord - a non-negative integer that specifies the x-coordinate of the field on the project's images. Coordinates are relative to the top-left corner of the image, zero-based, and measured in pixels.
        width - a positive integer that specifies the width of the field in the project's images, measured in pixels
        help_html - the location of an HTML file that contains end-user help for the field
        known_data - optional location of a text file containing known values for this field
